'''基督教中國佈道會聖道迦南書院'''（英語：ECF Saint Too Canaan College）是[[香港|香港]][[觀塘區|觀塘區]]的一間[[直接資助計劃|直資]][[香港英文授課中學|英文中學]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://topick.hket.com/article/2808012/ |title=【運動教學】聖道迦南書院積極推廣飛盤成種子中學　體育科主任：藉飛盤運動鍛鍊團隊協作精神 |access-date=2021-05-22 |archive-date=2021-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522084038/https://topick.hket.com/article/2808012 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/%E9%9D%9E%E8%8F%AF%E8%AA%9E-%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B8%E6%97%8F%E8%A3%94-%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87-170704 |title=十個學生如何改變一間學校？自己教材自己預備  |access-date=2021-05-22 |archive-date=2021-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522084039/https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/%e9%9d%9e%e8%8f%af%e8%aa%9e-%e5%b0%91%e6%95%b8%e6%97%8f%e8%a3%94-%e5%ad%b8%e4%b8%ad%e6%96%87-170704 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://happypama.mingpao.com/%E6%99%BA%E8%AD%98%E6%8F%80%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1/ |title=聖道迦南書院著重學業成就 培育謙卑公民 回饋社會  |access-date=2022-06-16 |archive-date=2021-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522091315/https://happypama.mingpao.com/%E6%99%BA%E8%AD%98%E6%8F%80%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1/ }}</ref>

學校有30間課室、1間特別室、一個禮堂、一個圖書館、兩個籃球場、一個健身室、有蓋操場和足球場（和[[匯基書院（東九龍）|匯基書院（東九龍）]]共用），是一所[[千禧校舍|千禧校舍]]。

== 班級結構 ==
以愛（Love）、望（Hope）、信（Faith）、誠（Honesty）為班別名稱。全校有24班。由2021-2022學年起，中一及中二級開設毅 (Perseverance)班，使全校增至有26班。

==校訓==
「Glorifying God, Edifying People　崇聖敬道　榮神益人」

學校的使命宣言：

藉着聖經真理，透過實踐愛的教育，建立充滿創意、積極進取、關懷互信的校園，協助學生建立和諧的社群關係，發揮獨特潛質，在知識、品德、情意方面成長，成為負責任、情理兼備、胸襟廣闊、追求卓越的青年人。 (Based on the teaching of the Bible and through the practice of love, we are committed to creating a learning environment filled with creativity, initiative, care and trust. We aim to help students build harmonious relationships with others, and to develop their own unique potential in the areas of intellect, character and temperament. We aspire to cultivate young people with a sense of responsibility, rationality and affection, who pursue excellence in life with vision and passion.)
;
;
;
;
; 鄰近設施

* 順利消防局
* [[佐敦谷公園|佐敦谷公園]]
* 順利邨遊樂場

